            <li>Resilient Networks</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="capability-card">
          <div class="capability-header">
            <h3>Autonomous Systems</h3>
            <span class="capability-icon">ü§ñ</span>
          </div>
          <p>Next-generation autonomous platforms with advanced AI decision-making. Unmanned systems for reconnaissance, logistics, and combat support.</p>
          <ul class="tech-list">
